     <h1 class="e-headline u-heading-1  " data-test="headline" itemprop="headline">Hiroshima: 70 years on, one survivor remembers the horror of the world's first atomic bombing</h1>
     <p class="e-standfirst u-heading-4 " itemprop="description" data-test="standfirst">As Japan marks 70 years since the Hiroshima and Nagasaki atom bombs, Yukiko Nakabushi talk about her crusade against nuclear weapons</p>
