       <span itemprop="caption" data-test="caption">A man stand on the debris after the atomic bomb completely destroyed Hiroshima in August 1945</span> <span class="e-caption__credit" itemprop="copyrightHolder" data-test="credit"> <span class="e-caption__credit-description">Credit</span>: Photo: Hajime Miyatake/Getty </span>
